{
  "id": "RAW_28299ceb",
  "title": "旁听了 OpenAI 首席战略官的分享，并带来一些纪要",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247508292&idx=1&sn=573601d9382766884765a79ecf316e96",
  "date": "2025-11-12 04:21:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dd0599cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2icSMc1VBIYoOjWT5hgnIMw84f3R10Th1CURfy7OYzVDtnvOWq35xUqSKJqG2dU5icITqiavs6xVRL7P00VibSdtOg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:12px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:8px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.067) 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.067) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 32px), repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.067) 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.067) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 32px) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">旁听了 OpenAI 首席战略官 Jason Kwon 的一场小范围分享，内容是关于<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&amp;mid=2247507610&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=fa61365303d606eac1b199356cde19e5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"公司最近完成的一次组织架构重组\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">公司最近完成的一次组织架构重组</a></span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 16px;margin:0px 8px 32px;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 4px 6px;border-width:0px 0px 0px 4px;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心信息</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 成立了一个新的非营利组织，叫 OpenAI 基金会。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个基金会反过来管理着一个新的营利实体，叫 OpenAI 集团，这是一家公益公司 (PBC)</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;\">Josh 提到，OpenAI 的旧结构设计时很理想，但实际运行后发现比预期\"creaky\"（吱嘎作响）得多，投资人每轮融资都得重新理解一遍这个从没见过的结构，摩擦很大&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;PBC（公益公司）这东西在特拉华州存在超过 10 年，有上市公司和很多私营公司在用：投资人看得懂，尽职调查省事</span></span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个基金会初始就持有 OpenAI 集团价值约&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1300 亿美金</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的股权</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键信息：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 0.2em;margin:0px 12px 16px 16px;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.8;list-style:disc;text-align:left;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">新结构</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：非营利基金会管理一家公益公司 (PBC)</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">直接动机</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：为 AI 研究需要的巨大算力，建立一个更高效的融资渠道</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">资产规模</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：基金会初始持有&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1300 亿美金</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的股权，并承诺先期投入&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">250 亿美金</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">用于公益项目</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">制衡机制</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：基金会下设的安全委员会，拥有对技术发布的最终安全决策权，且该决策只对使命负责</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"305\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYoK9h8gk64nJVLmwNTZwaPWAHFKHLlegDkuEaQLP9B3p3cVhDRRWHuemrBZSwicPibLXW4jLbH3Rctg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-imgfileid=\"100023950\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;border-style:solid;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;text-align:left;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;margin:0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67c52cb0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYoK9h8gk64nJVLmwNTZwaPWAHFKHLlegDkuEaQLP9B3p3cVhDRRWHuemrBZSwicPibLXW4jLbH3Rctg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&amp;mid=2247507610&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=fa61365303d606eac1b199356cde19e5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"前几天sam也直播谈到了这个话题\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">前几天sam也直播谈到了这个话题</a></span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <h3 style=\"margin:32px 8px 24px !important;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:18px;border-width:0px 0px 1px 4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid solid dashed;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">动机：旧结构的融资摩擦</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Jason Kwon 提到，变革的原因在于旧的“上限利润 (capped-profit)”结构</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个结构在几年的实践中，被证明在资本市场进行大规模融资时，会产生不小的摩擦</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于需要为基础设施和数据中心筹集巨额资金的 OpenAI 来说，这种摩擦带来的沟通成本和复杂性越来越高</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单来说，旧的结构在应对当前 AI 研究所需的资本时，显得效率不足（说人话：融资麻烦）</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以需要一次调整</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"margin:32px 8px 24px !important;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:18px;border-width:0px 0px 1px 4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid solid dashed;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">新方案：基金会与公益公司</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">新的方案由两部分组成</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">负责对接资本市场的是</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">PBC 公益公司</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;(Public Benefit Corporation, PBC)。这是一个投资人相对熟悉的法律实体结构，可以简化融资流程</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">负责确保使命的是非营利的 OpenAI 基金会。它 100% 控制着 PBC</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">基金会董事会的下面，设有</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">安全与保障委员会 (SSC)</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。根据其治理文件，这个委员会在做安全相关决策时，其法律上的信托责任只对“确保 AGI 造福全人类”这一使命负责，而不是对股东的商业利益负责</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">分享中也提到，这个基金会承诺先期投入&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">250 亿美金</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，用于两个方向：生物与健康领域的科学突破，以及 AI 适应力 (AI resilience) 生态的建设</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"margin:32px 8px 24px !important;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:18px;border-width:0px 0px 1px 4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid solid dashed;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个关于研究的故事</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">分享中，Jason Kwon 讲了一个他刚加入 OpenAI 时的小故事</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当时他觉得很难跟上研究部门的节奏，于是去找当时的研究副总裁 Bob McGrew，希望能多了解一些未来的规划，以便提前准备</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 16px;margin:0px 8px 32px;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 4px 6px;border-width:0px 0px 0px 4px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Bob McGrew 当时只是笑了笑，说：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“这是研究 (It’s research)”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Jason 表示，从那时起他便理解，这家公司的运营必须适应研究过程中的发现与意外（说人话：鬼特么知道会发生什么）</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: #c66e49;font-weight: bold;\">当前正在做的事情，可能在几个月后就不是重点了</span>，毕竟研究总有新发现</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也在一定程度上解释了 OpenAI 的工作方式：</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 16px;margin:0px 8px 32px;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 4px 6px;border-width:0px 0px 0px 4px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">由研究的走向，来决定下一步做什么</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，而不是严格遵循一个固定的产品路线图</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章纪要了 OpenAI 首席战略官 Jason Kwon 的分享，详细阐述了 OpenAI 为解决融资摩擦而进行的组织架构重组，即成立非营利基金会管理公益公司（PBC）。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章纪要了 OpenAI 首席战略官 Jason Kwon 的分享，详细阐述了 OpenAI 为解决融资摩擦而进行的组织架构重组，即成立非营利基金会管理公益公司（PBC）。",
  "summary": "文章记录了 OpenAI 首席战略官 Jason Kwon 关于公司近期组织架构重组的分享。核心内容指出，OpenAI 成立了一个新的非营利基金会，该基金会反过来管理着一个新的营利实体——OpenAI 集团（一家公益公司 PBC）。此次变革的直接动机是为了建立更高效的融资渠道，以满足 AI 研究对巨大算力的需求。旧的“上限利润”结构在实践中被证明在大规模融资时摩擦很大。新结构下，基金会初始持有 OpenAI 集团约 1300 亿美金的股权，并承诺先期投入 250 亿美金用于公益项目，并通过下设的安全委员会确保技术发布只对“AGI 造福全人类”的使命负责。文章还提及了 OpenAI“由研究走向决定下一步”的运营方式。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 重组为非营利基金会管理公益公司（PBC）的新结构",
      "explanation": "此举旨在优化融资效率，解决旧“上限利润”结构在获取大规模 AI 研究资金时遇到的摩擦，基金会持有巨额股权并承诺公益投入。"
    },
    {
      "point": "新结构通过制衡机制确保 AI 使命优先于商业利益",
      "explanation": "基金会下设的安全委员会拥有技术发布的最终安全决策权，其信托责任只对“AGI 造福全人类”的使命负责，而非股东利益。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 的运营模式是研究驱动而非产品路线图驱动",
      "explanation": "公司文化强调适应研究过程中的发现和意外，由研究进展来决定下一步的工作重点，体现了其对前沿探索的重视。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "OpenAI 成立了一个新的非营利组织，叫 OpenAI 基金会。这个基金会反过来管理着一个新的营利实体，叫 OpenAI 集团，这是一家公益公司 (PBC)",
    "OpenAI 的旧结构设计时很理想，但实际运行后发现比预期'creaky'（吱嘎作响）得多，投资人每轮融资都得重新理解一遍这个从没见过的结构，摩擦很大",
    "基金会下设的安全委员会，拥有对技术发布的最终安全决策权，且该决策只对使命负责",
    "由研究的走向，来决定下一步做什么，而不是严格遵循一个固定的产品路线图"
